### 1. Enable Rewriting
RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /smt-library/

### 2. Redirect for the Ontology
# Request: https://w3id.org/smt-library/ontology
RewriteRule ^ontology$ https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexWitches/semantic-tarot-library/main/ontology/smtOntology.ttl [R=302,L]

### 3. Redirect for the Knowledge Graph
# Request: https://w3id.org/smt-library/graph
RewriteRule ^kg$ https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexWitches/semantic-tarot-library/main/ontology/smtGraph.ttl [R=302,L]

### 4. Redirect for the Website
# Request: https://w3id.org/smt-library/
RewriteRule ^$ https://hexwitches.github.io/semantic-tarot-library/ [R=302,L]